    LlamaStack -.->|"web search<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"| TavilySearch["Tavily Search"]
    LlamaStack -.->|"observability<br/>4318/TCP HTTP"| OTelCollector["OTEL Collector"]

    %% Integration Points (Other RHOAI components → Llama Stack)
